{"tid":1169690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支爆沒事兒]支那銀保監會等接管包商銀行一年　因出現嚴重信用風險","createTime":"2019-05-24T14:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T14:14:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89351f33f057e062e21441d67fb46f5a6d223a96","tid":1169690,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"人民銀行、銀保監會聯合公布，由於包商銀行出現嚴重信用風險，為保護存戶和其他客戶合法權益，銀保監會等有關方面即日起接管包商銀行一年。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，包商銀行被接管後，人行、銀保監會和存款保險基金對個人儲蓄存款本息全額保障，個人存款自由等沒有變化，而各項存、貸、匯等業務不變，銀行卡照常使用。<br />\n<br />\n包商銀行前身是內蒙古包頭市商業銀行，該行約一年前指會引入戰略投資者，主要股東或會變動，因此不公布2017年報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459236-20190524.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459236-20190524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=da71a355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459236-20190524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9668f070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459236-20190524.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}